title: Omnopolis 01 - 03 (2007) (Dragonz) cbr
description:
I know that Mr. Charlie Chevrolet a little genius in quantum physics. I know he gets scholarships and that he has a coveted record in all headhunters who recruit for our competitors. But mostly what I know is that the prototype of the dimensional module he developed, will ruin us all. You have carte blanche to stop Chevrolet! All means are allowed!
All! But under no circumstances should he reach Omnopolis with the prototype!
You need to stop Charlie Chevrolet! At all costs!


enjoy
